We’ve seen #SeaKraken team broadcaster @thevoicefitz explore the PNW throughout his SightSEAing explorations, but now, in collaboration with @AlaskaAir, he ventures to a whole new world - Alaska.

Tune in this Friday as Fitz takes on the Final Frontier.
